&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "59",
&"next_id": "60",
&"text": "Oh you 🥰",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"6": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "6",
&"next_id": "7",
&"text": "Like 200 people in a room",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"60": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "60",
&"next_id": "61",
&"text": "Anyway her name is Nina",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"61": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "61",
&"next_id": "62",
&"text": "What's she like?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"62": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "62",
&"next_id": "63",
&"text": "Well she approached me",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"63": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "63",
&"next_id": "64",
&"text": "And she sort of put her arm around me like a hug from behind 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"64": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "64",
&"next_id": "65",
&"text": "She said something like \"Wow ur a cutie\"",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"65": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "65",
&"next_id": "66",
&"text": "I was like uhm... Uhh.. H-hello do I know you 😫",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"66": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "66",
&"next_id": "67",
&"text": "Wow 😂",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"67": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "67",
&"next_id": "68",
&"text": "She was so forward huh 😳",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"68": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "68",
&"next_id": "69",
&"text": "I felt my heart beating like crazy 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"69": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "69",
&"next_id": "70",
&"text": "Then she introduced herself and said that she was in the sorority",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"7": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "7",
&"next_id": "8",
&"text": "Haha mine was about the same",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"70": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "70",
&"next_id": "71",
&"text": "It was scary at first but she ended up being really excited to get my number and stuff",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"71": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "71",
&"next_id": "72",
&"text": "Oh good for you! First friend",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"72": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "72",
&"next_id": "73",
&"text": "I guess so 😅 Not how I expected it!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"73": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "73",
&"next_id": "74",
&"text": "Uhm Babe...",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"74": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "74",
&"next_id": "75",
&"text": "What's a sorority? 🙂",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"75": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "75",
&"next_id": "76",
&"text": "Well, its like a girls club almost",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"76": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "76",
&"next_id": "77",
&"text": "They have an interesting reputation to say the least",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"77": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "77",
&"next_id": "78",
&"text": "What do you mean?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"78": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "78",
&"next_id": "79",
&"text": "The one in this college is known for social events like parties and stuff",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"79": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "79",
&"next_id": "80",
&"text": "More party people?? 😫",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"8": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "8",
&"next_id": "9",
&"text": "Made any new friends yet?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"80": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "80",
&"next_id": "81",
&"text": "Well, I can't say I'm surprised",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"81": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "81",
&"next_id": "82",
&"text": "It's all everyone's been doing so far 😒",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"82": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "82",
&"next_id": "83",
&"text": "Well at least I made a friend I think",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"83": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "83",
&"next_id": "84",
&"text": "Maybe she could teach me how to survive college",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"84": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "84",
&"next_id": "85",
&"text": "She seemed pretty relaxed about the whole thing",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"85": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "85",
&"next_id": "86",
&"text": "That's great!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"86": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "86",
&"next_id": "87",
&"text": "Good friends are gonna make it all easier",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"87": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "87",
&"next_id": "88",
&"text": "I seriously feel like I'm one of those kids in kindergarten that realized their mom isn't in the room anymore 😭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"88": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "88",
&"next_id": "89",
&"text": "You'll be fine haha",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"89": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "89",
&"next_id": "90",
&"text": "Yeah... I think so 😊",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
