raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Hey partner!
Player: Heya!
Player: How was orientation?
Mabel: SO overwhelming though
Mabel: Like 200 people in a room
Player: Haha mine was about the same
Player: Made any new friends yet?
Mabel: I think I did! 🤩
Mabel: What about you?
Player: Same!
Mabel: Got a picture?
Mabel: Thought: I hope it's not a girl
Player: Of him? No 😂
Mabel: Thought: Phew
Mabel: I meant WITH him silly
Mabel: Oh is this like a boys and girls thing?
Player: Probably haha
Mabel: Well check us out 😎
Mabel: img: mabel/13
Player: Wow, she looks tough!
Mabel: She looks cool doesn't she!?
Mabel: Better keep up babe
Mabel: Delete: She might steal me from you
Mabel: Jk 🤭
- She might steal me too [#distrust]
	set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
	Player: She might steal me too 😂
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: Babe I was kiddinggg 😭
	Player: Hey I'm kidding too
	Mabel: You mean it? Say Promise
	- Or what? 😝 [#blackheart]
		set Story.flag = \"StolenByNina\"
		set Story.black_heart += 1
		set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
		Player: Or what? 😝
		Mabel: Babe I'm serious!
		Mabel: Say it 🥺
		Player: Fiiine, promise.
		Mabel: Thought: Hmph, meanie..
	- Promise! [#trust]
		set Story.mabel_trust += 1
		Player: Promise!
		Mabel: img: mabel/14
		Mabel: Hmph, you're teasing me too much today! 🥹
	Mabel: Okay then..
	Mabel: If you say so 😊
	do heart(0)
	Mabel: PinkThought: Nobody would ever steal me from you anyway
- She could never steal you from me [#love] [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: She could never steal you from me
	Mabel: Omg shush you're making me blush 😊
	Mabel: I was just teasing you
	Mabel: Why'd you have to be all cute suddenly 🫣
	Player: Mission accomplished hehe
	Mabel: Oh you 🥰
Mabel: Anyway her name is Nina
Player: What's she like?
Mabel: Well she approached me
Mabel: And she sort of put her arm around me like a hug from behind 😅
Mabel: She said something like \"Wow ur a cutie\"
Mabel: I was like uhm... Uhh.. H-hello do I know you 😫
Player: Wow 😂
Mabel: She was so forward huh 😳
Mabel: I felt my heart beating like crazy 😅
Mabel: Then she introduced herself and said that she was in the sorority
Mabel: It was scary at first but she ended up being really excited to get my number and stuff
Player: Oh good for you! First friend
Mabel: I guess so 😅 Not how I expected it!
Mabel: Uhm Babe...
Mabel: What's a sorority? 🙂
Player: Well, its like a girls club almost
Player: They have an interesting reputation to say the least
Mabel: What do you mean?
Player: The one in this college is known for social events like parties and stuff
Mabel: More party people?? 😫
Mabel: Well, I can't say I'm surprised
Mabel: It's all everyone's been doing so far 😒
Mabel: Well at least I made a friend I think
Mabel: Maybe she could teach me how to survive college
Mabel: She seemed pretty relaxed about the whole thing
Player: That's great!
Player: Good friends are gonna make it all easier
Mabel: I seriously feel like I'm one of those kids in kindergarten that realized their mom isn't in the room anymore 😭
Player: You'll be fine haha
Mabel: Yeah... I think so 😊
Mabel: PinkThought: I'll be fine knowing you're here
Mabel: sfx: bedcreak2: *creak*
Mabel: I'm gonna get some sleep now
Mabel: We have to be up early for tomorrow too
Mabel: So talk to you tomorrow okay? 😘
Player: Sure thing babe
Mabel: Good night! ❤️
Player: Nighty!
do queue_social_post(\"jason_drinking\")
do random_post(\"campus_life\")
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
